{
  "stem": "8234.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "For a while, we slept just on the floor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Work was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "At 4 o'clock, they wake us up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We went to the [NON-ENGLISH], which they built over there a huge network of railroads.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "About 100 railroads together, in a-- in a-- there's supposed to be a changing place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You see, trains came from all over the country, they-- they take off of their wagons and move them to-- to special rails, and-- and put them on the special trains.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they went all over-- all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were to build this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was-- we-- Polish Jews, there were a lot of Poles, but not prisoners.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were workers, and a lot of Germans, and British prisoners of war, and the hondons-- the first time I saw British.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were all captured in Dunkirk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Anyway, I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They chose me to be a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I used to move-- you see, to-- they did a lot of grading from ground to take off hills.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You had-- you had little trains with a lot a little wagons, and they used to fill with dirt, and move from place to place.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I used to move the trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let's see, I think oh, maybe we have to go left, I turn the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right, turn the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to remember which train is there, because if a train was running down the hill, I was suppose to stop the next train, and move them on a waiting line.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I made a mistake, it would kill me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- I managed this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the work wasn't hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes I had to shovel some coal through the-- through the wagons, because they weren't very good.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
